LAS VEGAS REVIEW-JOURNAL, Appellant,
v.
Steven B. WOLFSON, Clark County District Attorney, Respondent. No. 73457 Supreme Court of Nevada. APRIL 02, 2018

McLetchie Shell LLC

Clark County District Attorney/Civil Division

ORDER DISMISSING APPEAL

Pursuant to the stipulation of the parties, and cause appearing, this appeal is dismissed. The parties shall bear their own costs and attorney fees. NRAP 42(b).

It is so ORDERED.
